data.title: DEAD IDENTITIES
data.meta_description:
DEAD IDENTITIES.
London, UK.
Dead Identities are:
Keef - Vocals and Guitar
Toby - Lead Guitar and Vocals
Jimmy - Bass Guitar and Vocals
Jason - Drums and Vocals
Hailing from London, England Dead Identities have to-date released two full-length albums, 2007's Music From The Waiting Room and the long awaited follow up Bad Cats And Heart Attacks in 2010. The band are currently recording their as yet untitled third album.
